{"tid":2180132,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"其實只要幫美國人認清中共真面目, 就係助選好方法","createTime":"2020-08-29T15:26:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T14:43:37.000Z","uid":76310,"like":89,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"5fd5bd0aa859bf7a28a67cd33d74941cf819fc36","tid":2180132,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T15:26:33.000Z","msg":"現在美國人主要有三個考慮點: 疫情, 經濟, 中国事宜(排前有先後)<br />\n好正常, 人梗係諗自己健康和生命, 之後再諗工作, 錢同經濟, 當然之後先諗中国事宜<br />\n<br />\n其實幫美國人認清中共真面目, 就係助選好方法:<br />\n<br />\n国安法限制香港人自由<br />\n新疆集中營<br />\n種族清洗新疆人<br />\n將言論審查推向全世界<br />\n中国偷竊美國人知識產權<br />\n中国盜取美國人的工作<br />\n中国企圖取代美國<br />\n<br />\n雖然中国事宜唔係第一, 但只要黎緊呢二個疫情放緩, 經濟轉好, 中国事宜得到關注就會大大提升<br />\n所以大家努力繼續打好國際戰線, 幫美國人認清中共真面目, 就係助選好方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話唔定將來就係有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea1f258bedadd88b5b83d9004c9dd7dd095ae66b","tid":2180132,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T15:28:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1545eaf048947a6e20103b1fe68c81905dbfbc7c","tid":2180132,"uid":311337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T15:32:31.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8f2f7357eb7d6c7e1f2c07680c75661b78e2c525","tid":2180132,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T15:39:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"65ea5a31e9c212cd9a5d2503650d7b11a847453f","tid":2180132,"uid":329415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fd5bd0aa859bf7a28a67cd33d74941cf819fc36","tid":2180132,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2